<h6>Identify your singing level</h6>

dekhiye 10 level maine divide kar diye hai, to aapko pata karna hai aap kaunse level pe ho, wo aapka kaam hai.
main bataunga kaun kaun se level hote hai, lekin woh banane se pahle main aapko batana chahunga ki aapko jo level hai woh aapko khud identify karna hai.
agar aapko identify nahi ho raha hai, to aap apna voice sample mujhe fb id pe bhej sakte hai. main aapko bataunga aapka ki aap kaunse level hai. waise maine itana simplify kiya hai aap aaram se pata kar loge ki kaha se start karna hai singing aapko. pahle aapko uska level identify karna hai phir aapko pata chal jayega kaha se start karna hai.
<h6>First three levels are music theory: Introduction to music scale, read and write indian music</h6>
to sabase pahle ke 3 level hai, woh theory level aur 4 se level 10 tak practical level hai.
sabse pahla jo level hai aapko knowledge honi chahiye what is musical notes, matlab jo sur kya hai, uska naam kya hota hai, itani to knowledge honi hi chahiye. 
sabse pahle jo 2 level hai woh hai introduction of scales, usake baad 3rd level hai how to write and read music, indian classical music in hindi.
to yeh aapko pata hona chahiye ki kaise padha jata hai indian classical music, jo language hai usi language mein main aapse aage baat karunga. alankar aapko padhana hi nahi aayega to gaaoge kaise to aapko pata hona chahiye alankar kaise padha jata hai.
indian classical musical language woh kaisi hai, uska structure kaisa hai. abhi pahle ke jo 2 level hai, musical notes main already daal chuka hoon, iske baad jo 3rd level hai how to read and write music woh aage daalunga. 
<h6>4th Level: Pitch (Sur) matching</h6>
jo 4th level level hai waha se aapka practical start ho jayega, to 4th level hai pitch matching.
to pitch matching mein kya hota hai, koi bhi gaana aap gaate ho, koi bhi singer jab gaata hai jaise "chaunga main tujhe" to main huuunn gaya pahle. huuuunn kya hai. "sa" pakada maine pahle, yani koi gana baj raha hai. to uski scale pakadana hai, agar woh kar lete ho to aapki pitch matching achchhi hai.
par agar aap nahi kar pate ho, matlab gaana kisi aur scale mein baj raha hai aur aap kisi aur scale mein gaa rahe ho, to usko out of pitch bolate hai.
woh aana sabse jaroori hai. sabse pahle practical step hai woh yeh hai, level mein 4 pe aayega. 
<h6>Level 5: Singing in rhythm (Taal) throughout the song</h6>
phir level 5 mein aayega singing in rhythm through out the song. usake baad aage continue kare. taal mein gana nahi aata hai to bahoot bada issue hai yeh. uska bhi separate lesson aur pitch matching lesson. in sabka main seperate details lesson banaunga aur maximum simplify karne ki koshish karonga.
aur kuch nayi techniques bataunga jo kaam karegi. iske baad jo hai, woh singing melodiously throughout the song, jo 6th level hai. 
poore gaane mein ek bahoot bada issue hai, starting mein kya hota hai, gala besura ho jata hai gaate gaate. 100% melody honi chahiye through out the song, yani kahi bhi sur hilana nahi chahiye. 
