<h6>Feelings, Harkat & Murkiya, Voice Range</h6>
how to feel the song woh main already daal chuka hoon. uske baad aayega harkat, singing with harkat & murkiya. uske baad aayega vocal range,  bottom range and upper range. yani jo neeche ki range hai aur jo upper ki range hai. woh aapko aana chahiye. uske baad vibrato achchha hona chahiye. 10 level vibrato hai 9 level range hai. 8 level how to sing harkat & murkiya in the song, how to feel the song usake baad hai. 6 melodiously gaana aana chahiya, 5 singing in rhythm throughout the song, 4 hai singing with pitch matching.
<h6>Don't jump, progress step by step</h6>
ab main jo bolane ja raha hon, dhyaan se sun lijiye, kisi bhi level pe aap hai, maan lijiye, main melodiously gaa nahi paata hoon, sur hilata hai, aur mujhe kaam karna hai, sur ko intact karne ka, ek baar sur intact hoga, to hi aap aage ke level mein jayege.
maine bahoot sare aise singers dekhe hai jo vocal range pe kaam kar rahe hai aur usko sample mangata hoon to dekhata hoon ki gaane mein sur hi nahi hai. gaane mein sur itana jyada hil raha hai, ki bahoot jyda work karne ki jaroorat hai us par.
