9th level pe range ko rakh raha hoon aur 10th level pe vibrato hai, pata nahi kyon log karna chahte hai isko. par sabse pahle neeche ke levels clear kar lijiye.
yeh sab jab clear hoge to hi aap 9th aur 10th pe aayiye. jo bhi level aap identify karoge, poori tarike se aap master nahi jaate aap aage nahi badhoge. kyonki aage nahi badh sakte, jab tak is step ko clear nahi karoge.
