<h6>Falsetto, voice range, vocal expressions</h6>
koi falsetto mein gana chah raha hai. chalo main falsetto mein gana bata doon phir aap falsetto ke bhi nahi rahoge aur jo riyaz besura ke liye kar rahe ho, to usake bhi nahi rahoge. main voice sample mangata hoon aur voice sample achchha hai to main bolata hoon you are on the track aur uske baad aap aage ki cheeze hai woh kar sakte hai. lekin log kah rahe hai main falsetto karna chahata hoon par jab voice sample mangata hoon to dekhata hoon melody hi nahi hai, taal hi nahi hai, poora gana besura hai. pahle yeh sab badi badi cheeze hai us par kaam karna chalu kijiye hai, yeh jo additional cheeze hai yeh baad ki cheeze hai.
<h6>Can any body learn singing? Type1 Singer & Type2 Singer</h6>
ek aur important cheez batani hai, yeh ek bahoot bada confusion hai ki har koi singing kar sakta hai. actually mere hisab se koi bhi singing kar sakta hai, main is par believe nahi karta ki koi bhi singing nahi kar sakta hai. lekin ab jo aa raha hai, problem kya hai, 2 tarah ki singer hote hai ek type 1 singer hote hai aur doosare type 2.
type 1 ka jo singer hota hai woh garbh se nikata hai, womb se nikata hai, uska jo vocal structure hota hai, vocal chord ka structure hota hai woh already achchha hota hai. uska gala already 6 level pe hoga. yani melody uske gale mein intact hogi. matlab usko melody pe kaam karna jaroori nahi hai. agar aap 6 level pe ho to aage ki cheeze jaldi jaldi aayegi. matlab harkat ho gaya, range ho gaya, vibrato ho gaya. lekin aap 6 level pe nahi ho. to bahoot problem hota hai. type 1 ke singer 6 level pe hi paida hota hai. matlab bachpan se hi sur mein gaate ha. jaise main type 1 singer hoon. to bachpan mein hi meri mummy bolati thi main twinkle twinkle little star  jiggle gata tha. humesha sur mein gata tha. sur hilata nahi tha mera. uske baad aise singer jo hote hai. unko bola jata hai. aapki upar ishwar ki kripa hai. god has blessed you with singing skill. matlab aap singing karne ke liye paida hue ho.
<h6>Type 2 Singer need more motivation & patience</h6>
leking yeh galat hai ki baki ke jo log bache hai, jo type 2 mein aate hai woh singing nahi kar sakte hai. aisa galat hai, type 2 singer hai bachpan se uske gale mein melody intact nahi hoti hai. to gale mein melody lana unka pahla goal hona chahiye. log kya kar rahe hai vocal range ki taraf bhaag rahe hai, falsetto ki taraf bhaag rahe hai. type 2 singer humesha bahoot jyada time leta hai kyonki use bahoot jyada motivation ki jaroorat hoti hai, patience ki jaroorat hoti hai. agar aapke andar interest, passion hai to aap kar loge. kyonki usko time bahoot lagta hai.
jo type 2 level singer hota hai woh track mein nahi hota hai. ek baar level 6 pe aa gaya to uski gaadi track par hai. matlab melody throughout the song aa jaye. par usko track mein lane mein bahoot jyada mehnat ki jaroorat padti hai. type 1 singer ko time kam lagta hai. par type 2 singer ko gaane mein melody laane mein bahoot time lagta hai. kyonki unko ek ek note pe kaam karna hota hai. 
